    "description": "<u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cyborg Battles</h2></u><br>加入Novastride的战斗——你文明的命运就在你的肩膀上！与你的机器人战友一起战斗，获得胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/7e041cf7d028469cc2baaed1368723e3.poster.avif?t=1708632782\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/7e041cf7d028469cc2baaed1368723e3.webm?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/7e041cf7d028469cc2baaed1368723e3.mp4?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >High-Flying Action</h2></u><br>参加空中格斗！Novastride提供了令人兴奋的空中战斗和惊人的图形，带来了前所未有的沉浸式飞行体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/56dd3a98a81cb1262d1ea6837088dba7.poster.avif?t=1708632782\" width=800 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/56dd3a98a81cb1262d1ea6837088dba7.webm?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/56dd3a98a81cb1262d1ea6837088dba7.mp4?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich Story</h2></u><br>探索Novastride广阔的城市，揭示充满阴谋和危险的丰富、沉浸式故事！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/b4efdd8234fe0ef832bf7db9a0912bc5.poster.avif?t=1708632782\" width=800 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/b4efdd8234fe0ef832bf7db9a0912bc5.webm?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/b4efdd8234fe0ef832bf7db9a0912bc5.mp4?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense Space Experience</h2></u><br>开始前所未有的星际之旅，在那里你可以探索广阔的太空深处并参加令人兴奋的太空战斗！Novastride提供了一个沉浸式的太空模拟体验，让你探索从流浪行星到恒星系统的各种大气环境。当你穿越星际并遭遇敌对文明时，你的民族的命运将会悬在一线。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/5d5f591f6918a71d8846e73b532d3e1b.poster.avif?t=1708632782\" width=800 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/5d5f591f6918a71d8846e73b532d3e1b.webm?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/5d5f591f6918a71d8846e73b532d3e1b.mp4?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of Mechanics</h2></u><br>无缝地融合了令人兴奋的机制、沉浸式的支线任务和心跳加速的动作序列。在广阔的开放世界中探索，无尽的冒险可能性，Novastride是终极的太空模拟器。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/585a4d81d89b66770b6297beb9a63997.poster.avif?t=1708632782\" width=800 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/585a4d81d89b66770b6297beb9a63997.webm?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366350/extras/585a4d81d89b66770b6297beb9a63997.mp4?t=1708632782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
